'''Cameron A. Clarke''' ([[6 November|November 6]], [[1957]]) is an American voice actor. He voiced [[Arveleg I|King Arveleg]] in ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Battle for Middle-earth II: The Rise of the Witch-king|EA's The Battle for Middle-earth II: The Rise of the Witch-king]]'' and provided additional voices in ''[[The Hobbit (2003 video game)|The Hobbit]]''.
